Detailed Description

cvmx_ipd_port_qos_int#

See the description for IPD_PORT_QOS_X_CNT 0=P0-7; 1=P8-15; 2=P16-23; 3=P24-31; 4=P32-39; 5=P40-47; 6=P48-55; 7=P56-63 Only ports used are: P0-3, p16-19, P24, P32-39. Therefore only IPD_PORT_QOS_INT0 ([63:32] == Reserved), IPD_PORT_QOS_INT2 ([63:32] == Reserved), IPD_PORT_QOS_INT3 ([63:8] == Reserved), IPD_PORT_QOS_INT4
